Did that hurt?

00:48:37.250 --> 00:48:38.240
Did I...

00:48:38.830 --> 00:48:40.460
Did I go too hard on you?

00:48:43.530 --> 00:48:44.770
No.

00:48:45.740 --> 00:48:46.750
I like it.

00:48:47.610 --> 00:48:48.810
Like what?

00:48:49.340 --> 00:48:50.920
What I did,

00:48:51.510 --> 00:48:52.390
or me?

00:48:56.680 --> 00:48:57.840
Well..

00:48:59.790 --> 00:49:01.210
Both, I guess.

00:49:07.390 --> 00:49:08.980
Go to sleep.

00:49:08.980 --> 00:49:10.600
We have to wake up early.

00:49:14.490 --> 00:49:16.520
I don’t want to sleep yet.

00:49:17.490 --> 00:49:19.160
Then what do you want to do?

00:49:21.890 --> 00:49:22.710
Well…

00:49:27.630 --> 00:49:30.660
Do… that.

00:49:31.140 --> 00:49:31.940
Which?

00:49:34.420 --> 00:49:35.020
Um...

00:49:38.420 --> 00:49:40.000
That thing...

00:49:45.280 --> 00:49:46.700
Please?

00:49:47.280 --> 00:49:47.970
Please?

00:49:52.540 --> 00:49:53.620
Or…

00:49:53.910 --> 00:49:55.320
Are you already worn out?

00:50:02.720 --> 00:50:04.030
Should I do it for you?

00:50:09.050 --> 00:50:11.390
Do you want me to do it?

00:50:11.390 --> 00:50:12.810
No.

00:50:14.220 --> 00:50:15.490
What are you doing?

00:50:15.490 --> 00:50:16.510
Hey!

00:50:16.510 --> 00:50:17.980
I can do it.

00:50:17.980 --> 00:50:19.380
No.

00:50:23.420 --> 00:50:25.200
What did you just do to me?

00:50:25.200 --> 00:50:26.600
What?

00:50:27.820 --> 00:50:28.820
Don't be stubborn.

00:50:28.820 --> 00:50:30.000
Don't be stubborn.

00:50:30.000 --> 00:50:31.170
Still being stubborn?

