Calls just to say that and hangs up.

00:51:06.980 --> 00:51:07.760
What’s wrong with him?

00:51:15.400 --> 00:51:17.030
Sasom

00:51:17.030 --> 00:51:19.150
Woraphatcharakorn

00:51:19.390 --> 00:51:21.470
